/-- The inverse in the group is equal to the inverse given by `category_theory.inv`. -/
theorem vertex_group.inv_eq_inv (c : C) (γ : «expr ⟶ » c c) : γ⁻¹ = CategoryTheory.inv γ :=
  Groupoid.inv_eq_inv γ
